title: Independent candidate Tanveer Aslam wins PP-19 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Muhammad Tanveer Aslam has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-19, Rawalpindi-XIII by securing 43,987 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League (N) candidate, Haji Parvez Khan who bagged 16,768 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 42.69%.
